{"tid":2458824,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀中伏salon","createTime":"2021-03-23T17:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T01:34:26.000Z","uid":248768,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4a48f666456006c48e89dd5d05cf4358211ce1d0","tid":2458824,"uid":248768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T17:26:04.000Z","msg":"希望大家小心呢間salon <br />\n唔好好似我咁唔好彩<br />\n<br />\n本來洗剪吹+電髮$620<br />\n俾佢不停sell我用貴啲藥水 <br />\n話我頭髮好爛 如果唔用貴啲既藥水電($800) 個頭會好傷同唔攣<br />\n好啦 百幾蚊就聽佢講用貴啲既藥水<br />\n<br />\n結果電廿分鐘就話電完<br />\n剪一刀就話剪左(其實我見唔到佢剪個髮型亦都冇變化 但佢話剪咗)<br />\n電完個頭係奇怪攣<br />\n第二日洗完頭變返直髮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeYwmp1pzsf23L14CUZLhipnxudxE9FwX3QmPp2DsU3Re?filename=GgEuQHf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGgEuQHf.png&h=7d7ae6f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e041b1f52f99239c9f2b7ec861daa6340f2e414","tid":2458824,"uid":71657,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T17:27:08.000Z","msg":"唔幫襯黃店預咗㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27fa6d57d508ebe420ea0e9538a43756005bf11","tid":2458824,"uid":248768,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9e041b1f52f99239c9f2b7ec861daa6340f2e414","tid":2458824,"uid":71657,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T17:27:08.000Z","msg":"唔幫襯黃店預咗㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T17:28:58.000Z","msg":"佢自稱黃店"},{"pid":"f6aed86b075b91fc324cf986f9a4bc26b28c17e5","tid":2458824,"uid":248768,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T17:30:46.000Z","msg":"佢話幫我電呢款<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXESCiJnqtKd68YnSL2zvTgPrnqg1c8J4GgHTNMAB79X6?filename=560NCrc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F560NCrc.png&h=c56150a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果係<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ip